Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.58,0:01:45.54,Sign,,0,0,0,,Flower blooms... {On the morning of December 8, 1941, at the same time as the attack on Pearl Harbor, the 23rd Army Squadron launched its first air strike against British aircraft at Kai Tak Airfield. The telegram of the war order was coded "Hanasaku Hanasaku" - I... don't know why such code has been chosen and what it's supposed to symbolize}
